\c 10
\s UJehu uchitha indlu kaAhabi
\p
\v 1 Njalo uAhabi wayelamadodana angamatshumi ayisikhombisa eSamariya\x + 1 Kho. 16.24.\x*. UJehu wasebhala izincwadi, wazithumela eSamariya kubabusi beJizereyeli, abadala, lakubondli ba\add madodana\add* kaAhabi, esithi:
\v 2 Ngakho-ke nxa lincwadi ifika kini, lokhu amadodana enkosi yenu akini, futhi izinqola lamabhiza kukini, lomuzi obiyelweyo, lezikhali,
\v 3 ziboneleni-ke ongcono kakhulu lofaneleyo kulabo bonke ebantwaneni benkosi yenu, limbeke esihlalweni sobukhosi sikayise, lilwele indlu yenkosi yenu.
\v 4 Kodwa besaba kakhulukazi bathi: Khangelani, amakhosi amabili kawemanga phambi kwakhe; thina-ke sizakuma njani?
\v 5 Umphathi wendlu lomphathi womuzi labadala labondli \add babantwana\add* bathumela kuJehu besithi: Siyizinceku zakho, sizakwenza konke okutshoyo kithi. Kasiyikubeka muntu abe yinkosi. Yenza okuhle emehlweni akho\x + Josh. 9.8,11.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Wasebabhalela incwadi okwesibili esithi: Uba lingabami, lilalela ilizwi lami, thathani amakhanda alawomadoda, amadodana enkosi yenu, lize kimi eJizereyeli ngalesisikhathi kusasa. Lamadodana enkosi, abantu abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa, ayelezikhulu zomuzi ezaziwakhulisa.
\v 7 Kwasekusithi ekufikeni kwencwadi kubo, bathatha amadodana enkosi, babulala abantu abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa, bafaka amakhanda awo ezitsheni, ba\add w\add*esa kuye eJizereyeli\x + Hlab. 81.6. Jer. 24.1,2.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Kwasekusiza isithunywa sambikela sisithi: Sebewalethile amakhanda amadodana enkosi. Wasesithi: Abekeni abe zinqumbi ezimbili ekungeneni kwesango kuze kube sekuseni.
\v 9 Kwasekusithi ekuseni waphuma wema wathi ebantwini bonke: Lina lilungile. Khangelani, mina ngenzela inkosi yami ugobe, ngayibulala; pho, ngubani obulele bonke laba\x + 9.14,24.\x*?
\v 10 Yazini khathesi ukuthi kakuyikuwela lutho emhlabathini okwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalikhuluma ngendlu kaAhabi\x + 1 Sam. 3.19.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yenzile eyakukhulumayo ngesandla senceku yayo uElija\x + 1 Kho. 21.19,21,29.\x*.
\v 11 UJehu wasetshaya bonke ababesele endlini kaAhabi eJizereyeli, lazo zonke izikhulu zakhe, labazana laye, labapristi bakhe\x + 2 Sam. 20.26 .\x*, akaze amtshiyela oseleyo\x + Josh. 10.28.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Wasesukuma wahamba waya eSamariya. Endlini yokugunda yabelusi endleleni,
\v 13 uJehu wahlangana labafowabo bakaAhaziya inkosi yakoJuda\x + 8.29. 9.16. 2 Lan. 21.17. 2 Lan. 22.8.\x*, wathi: Lingobani? Basebesithi: Singabafowabo bakaAhaziya, sehlela ukubingelela abantwana benkosi, labantwana bendlovukazi\x + 1 Kho. 11.19.\x*.
\v 14 Wasesithi: Babambeni bephila. Basebebabamba bephila, bababulalela emgodini weBeti-Ekedi, amadoda angamatshumi amane lambili, katshiyanga loyedwa wabo.
\p
\v 15 Esesukile lapho wahlangana loJehonadabi\x + Jer. 35.6.\x* indodana kaRekabi \add eze\add*mhlangabeza\x + 1 Lan. 2.55.\x*; wambingelela wathi kuye: Inhliziyo yakho iqondile yini, njengoba inhliziyo yami ikanye lenhliziyo yakho? UJehonadabi wasesithi: Injalo. Uba kunjalo, \add ngi\add*pha isandla sakho. Wase\add m\add*nika isandla sakhe; wasemkhweza enqoleni kuye\x + Ezra 10.19. Hez. 17.18. 1 Lan. 29.24.\x*.
\v 16 Wasesithi: Hamba lami, ubone ukuyitshisekela kwami iN\nd kosi\x + 1 Kho. 19.10.\x*\nd*. Basebemgadisa enqoleni yakhe.
\v 17 Ekufikeni kwakhe eSamariya wabatshaya bonke ababesele kuAhabi eSamariya waze wamqeda, njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\x + 9.8.\x*\nd* eyalikhuluma kuElija\x + 10.10.\x*.
\s UJehu uqeda inkonzo kaBhali koIsrayeli
\p
\v 18 UJehu wasebuthanisa bonke abantu, wathi kibo: UAhabi wakhonza kancinyane uBhali: UJehu uzamkhonza kakhulu\x + 1 Kho. 16.31,32.\x*.
\v 19 Ngakho-ke ngibizelani abaprofethi bakaBhali bonke, izinceku zakhe zonke labo bonke abapristi bakhe, kungabi lamuntu ongekho, ngoba ngilomhlatshelo omkhulu kuBhali; loba ngubani ongayikuba khona kayikuphila. Kodwa uJehu wakwenza ngobuqili ukuze abulale izinceku zikaBhali\x + 1 Kho. 18.19. 22.6.\x*.
\v 20 UJehu wasesithi: Mehlukaniseleni umhlangano onzulu uBhali\x + Levi 23.36.\x*. Basebewumemezela\x + Eks. 32.5.\x*.
\v 21 UJehu wasethumela kuye wonke uIsrayeli; zonke izinceku zikaBhali zasezisiza, kakwaze kwasala loyedwa ongabuyanga. Bangena endlini kaBhali, yaze yagcwala indlu kaBhali kusukela emsamo kusiya emnyango\x + 10.26. 11.18. 1 Kho. 16 . 32.\x*.
\v 22 Wasesithi kulowo owayephethe indlu yezembatho: Khuphela bonke abakhonzi bakaBhali izembatho. Wasebakhuphela izembatho\x + Mat. 22.11.\x*.
\v 23 Wasengena uJehu eloJehonadabi indodana kaRekabi endlini kaBhali, wathi kuzinceku zikaBhali: Hlolani libone ukuthi kakukho kini abezinceku zeN\nd kosi\nd* lapha, kodwa izinceku zikaBhali kuphela.
\v 24 Sebengene ukwenza imihlatshelo leminikelo yokutshiswa, uJehu wazimisela amadoda angamatshumi ayisificaminwembili ngaphandle, wasesithi: Umuntu oyekela kumadoda engiwabeka ezandleni zenu iphunyuke, impilo yakhe izakuba sendaweni yempilo yayo\x + 1 Kho. 20.39,42.\x*.
\v 25 Kwasekusithi eseqedile ukwenza iminikelo yokutshiswa, uJehu wasesithi kubalindi lezinduneni\x + 11.4,6. 1 Sam. 22.17.\x*: Ngenani libatshaye, kungaphumi muntu. Basebebatshaya ngobukhali benkemba\x + 1 Kho. 18.40.\x*; abalindi lezinduna basebe\add ba\add*phosela phandle, baya emzini wendlu kaBhali\x + 11.4,6. 1 Sam. 22.17.\x*.
\v 26 Bakhupha endlini kaBhali insika eziyizithombe, bazitshisa.
\v 27 Badiliza insika kaBhali eyisithombe, badiliza indlu kaBhali, bayenza yaba yindlu yokuyela ngaphandle kuze kube lamuhla\x + Ezra 6.11. Dan. 2.5. 3.29.\x*.
\v 28 Ngokunjalo uJehu wachitha uBhali wamkhupha koIsrayeli.
\p
\v 29 Kodwa \add e\add*zonw\add eni\add* zikaJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati owenza uIsrayeli one, uJehu kasukanga ekuzilandeleni\x + 1 Kho. 14.16.\x*, amathole egolide ayeseBhetheli lawayekoDani\x + 1 Kho. 12.28,29.\x*.
\v 30 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuJehu: Ngoba wenze kuhle ngokwenza okulungileyo emehlweni ami, wenza endlini kaAhabi njengakho konke okwakusenhliziyweni yami, amadodana akho kuze kube \add sesizukulwaneni\add* sesine azahlala esihlalweni sobukhosi sakoIsrayeli\x + 15.12. 10.35. 13.1,10. 14.23. 15.8.\x*.
\v 31 Kodwa uJehu kaqaphelisanga ukuhamba emlayweni weN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, ngenhliziyo yakhe yonke; kasukanga ezonweni zikaJerobhowamu owenza uIsrayeli one\x + 1 Kho. 14.16.\x*.
\p
\v 32 Ngalezonsuku iN\nd kosi\nd* yaqala ukuquma isusa koIsrayeli\x + 13.25. 14.25.\x*. UHazayeli wasebatshaya kuyo yonke imingcele yakoIsrayeli\x + 8.12. 1 Kho. 19.17.\x*,
\v 33 kusukela eJordani empumalanga, ilizwe lonke leGileyadi, abakoGadi labakoRubeni labakoManase, kusukela eAroweri engasesifuleni seArinoni\x + Dute. 2.36.\x*, leGileyadi leBashani\x + Amos 1.3.\x*.
\p
\v 34 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJehu, lakho konke akwenzayo, lamandla akhe wonke, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli\x + Amos 1.3.\x*?
\v 35 UJehu waselala laboyise, bamngcwabela eSamariya. UJehowahazi indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 36 Lesikhathi uJehu abusa ngaso phezu kukaIsrayeli eSamariya sasiyiminyaka engamatshumi amabili lesificaminwembili.
